	<clause id="the_catd_comt_structure_and_format" obligation="normative"><title>The CATD-COMT Structure and Format</title><p id="_3950dbba-66e9-47c8-9355-1779e49357c2">The DSID information stored in the CATD-COMT field is subdivided into four or five comma separated subfields. This is dependant on whether the ENC file has an EN or ER application profile. The final subfield is punctuated by a semi colon (;).</p>
