	<clause id="process_oem_application" obligation="normative"><title>Process OEM Application</title><p id="_d6d0fa46-b894-41c5-8aed-19adf63065ab">Manufacturers must apply to the SA to become a member of the IHO S-63 Data Protection Scheme.</p>
	<clause id="issue_and_manage_s63_manufacturer_codes" obligation="normative">
	<title>Issue and Manage S-63 Manufacturer Codes</title>
	<p id="_7d054279-a40a-4f91-a733-d44e14ecf9e9">Successful OEM applicants will be supplied with their own unique Manufacturer ID (M_ID) and Manufacturer Key (M_KEY) see <xref target="m_id_format"/> and <xref target="m_key_format"/>. These codes must be stored securely together with the manufacturers contact details and whether they are still an active participant in the scheme.</p>
	</clause>
